
Installation:

 1. Get http://www.unixuser.org/~euske/pub/CMap.tar.bz2
 2. $ tar jxf CMap.tar.bz2
 3. $ make cdbcmap


Dump the contents:

  $ ./dumppdf.py foo.pdf

Extract the text:

  $ ./pdf2txt.py foo.pdf > foo.xml


